The icons are arranged in a circular pattern at the top, with the Google search bar. Below the circular icons, there is a section titled "All apps" with various app icons, such as Calendar, Camera, Chrome, Clock, Contacts, Drive, Files, Gmail, Google, Maps, Messages, Phone, Photos, Play Music, Settings, WebView, YouTube, and YT Music. The screen also shows a notification bar at the top with the current time and other icons.
